# HEALTH ASSIST ROBOT  
A smart IoT-powered hospital service robot designed to deliver **medicines, food, and water** to patients, equipped with **live camera feed**, **temperature monitoring**, **medicine queue system**, and **manual remote control**.

---

##  Overview  
Health Assist Robot reduces workload on nurses by automating the delivery of patient essentials.  
Using ESP32 + ESP32-CAM + Motor driver + Servos + Temperature sensors, the robot can:

- Take patient orders  
- Store them in a queue  
- Move through hospital rooms  
- Dispense medicine for a selected bed  
- Stream live video  
- Display real-time temperature  

---

##  Features  
✔ Medicine order system  
✔ Live ESP32-CAM video streaming  
✔ Motor control via W/A/S/D  
✔ Temperature sensor panel  
✔ Queue management system  
✔ Medicine dispenser (bed-wise)  
✔ Fully web-based UI  
✔ Responsive mobile interface  

