---

##  Hardware Used  
- ESP32 Dev Module  
- ESP32-CAM  
- L298N Motor Driver  
- MG996R Servo Motors  
- MG90S Micro Servos  
- 4 × Hub Motors  
- 12V Battery  
- DS18B20 Temperature Sensor  
- DHT11 Humidity Sensor  
- Food Heater Pad  
- Jumper wires, chassis, acrylic sheets

---

##  Software Used  
- Arduino IDE  
- ESP32 Core  
- HTML + CSS + JavaScript  
- WebServer Library  
- DallasTemperature Library  
- OneWire Library  


